      <title>达美航空预计第二季度利润和销售额将超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/delta-forecasts-2q-profit-sales-to-beat-expectations-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于夏季旅游旺季之前商务旅行的增加和休闲需求的稳定，达美航空预计第二季度利润和收入将超过华尔街的预测。彭博资讯 (Bloomberg Intelligence) 的乔治·弗格森 (George Ferguson) 在彭博电视台 (Bloomberg Television) 上有更多报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/delta-forecasts-2q-profit-sales-to-beat-expectations-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:58:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行存款自 2017 年以来首次跌破 4000 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ecb-deposits-fall-below-400-billion-for-first-time-since-2017</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区央行的存款自 2017 年以来首次降至 4000 亿欧元以下，因为当局继续为闲置资金寻求收益更高的住房。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ecb-deposits-fall-below-400-billion-for-first-time-since-2017</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:54:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
