    <item>
      <title>标准普尔因销售和利润疲软而将万科评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/s-p-downgrades-china-vanke-to-junk-on-weakening-sales-margins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级将万科公司的评级下调至垃圾级，突显这家国有开发商面临着越来越大的压力，因为该公司面临着现金短缺和投资者日益严格的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/s-p-downgrades-china-vanke-to-junk-on-weakening-sales-margins</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:21:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着油价上涨，投资者从石油基金撤资 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/investors-pull-2-billion-from-oil-fund-as-prices-extend-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于原油期货的涨势没有结束的迹象，投资者在过去 10 个月中从曾经最大的石油交易所交易基金中撤资约 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/investors-pull-2-billion-from-oil-fund-as-prices-extend-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 11:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管竞争对手因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎，宝马电动汽车销量仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马公司其核心品牌的全电动汽车销量在第一季度大幅增长，表现优于特斯拉和大众等竞争对手，后者一直在努力应对疲软的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
